<normalizedToken id="58E6135BB605E8FD1ECF70EB466EECF4" originalValue="Gewöhnliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Gewoehnliche</normalizedToken>
Kugelkopfbinse
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="15699D6A3EE77EB82249B499955C4280" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" type="description">
<paragraph id="8F48AAF41DBA36B96AA1CBAFD6FE5128" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
100-150 cm hoch. Rhizom unterirdisch kriechend, darauf in dichter Reihe die Stengel. 
<emphasis id="CD26B99CB2D8C1FAC675713122E20CEC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Meist keine deutlich ausgebildeten Blattspreiten vorhanden; unterste</emphasis>
(spreitenlose) 
<emphasis id="E0AA3102CC1272D91C8BAE3D48378D84" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Blattscheiden bis 8 cm lang</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="5FEEBDCF5288590071522F84312B094E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<pageBreakToken id="586B30BF876614AADB4C3E7FF3CE6B05" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">breit</pageBreakToken>
, braun. Die meisten Stengel am Grunde oberhalb der Blattscheiden mehr als 2,5 mm
</emphasis>
(bis 8 mm) 
<emphasis id="8DF4B4B641134E32B55401A95F940C51" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
dick. Hochblatt 1-2mal so lang wie der 
<normalizedToken id="FB4CB15A8F7EAB1875210D3BDFCF8F89" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="D54E39C18B844DFE4B7F3C287CB30B2A" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
aus 5-10 kugeligen 
<normalizedToken id="C4CF7922DAB36B3C1B173F699DD0B9ED" originalValue="Köpfen" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Koepfen</normalizedToken>
. Reife Frucht ca. 1 mm lang, scharf 3kantig. - 
<normalizedToken id="A6A329A29DD7400B61BD4FC4F2072A71" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E474C3A3161AC67467A1F4AC8A6979EA" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="644BBE39499BD47066E3E0E3C6847D45" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Zytologische Angaben. 2n ca. 164</emphasis>
(Fahmy aus 
<normalizedToken id="2000EBA055D0F0FA65557BEF2A0DDCB8" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="B0EEB6DEEB1B0DF02973CD9E94EF0DAD" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7FAAC9EEA25182070AE52720A02CC774" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="D2896E137A2A123A5E06137213100741" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Seeufer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A941CA3ECFE4966DE147CF1D7DB0F84B" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="2EEEFD9B9375C92CE273C59606B31D1C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Verbreitung. Mediterran-westasiatische Pflanze:</emphasis>
In 
<taxonomicName id="8F44F6BD4D231EC4C91858B163CDE76A" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Europa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Europa</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="26BAD1F0C76E141C52AA84F5C5858404" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="58F47BA6D588420D1427CBCA381F00AC" originalValue="Südengland" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Suedengland</normalizedToken>
, Norddeutschland (vereinzelt), 
<normalizedToken id="D3BB4E21BBD2A620C43C2ACD9CC019E5" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">haeufig</normalizedToken>
im Mediterrangebiet, durch 
<normalizedToken id="A84E63AB351FFDE56843CDC3E729EF16" originalValue="Südrußland" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Suedrussland</normalizedToken>
und den Kaukasus 
<normalizedToken id="6FCB6114ECB5C661BD9D96F1BDA99387" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Zentralasien; 
<normalizedToken id="A3068E4A8A3F6D33202F8FDBF216F310" originalValue="Südafrika" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Suedafrika</normalizedToken>
. - Im Gebiet: Genfersee (Sciez in Savoyen).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="691D2D2D1A32856FBE18D2AD8BE9C98B" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="63712108B25D5E5F1FD682CB44E07C60" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Siehe unter 
<taxonomicName id="69062350AF9F2E95EB7AF9516AB27DAC" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Holoschoenus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="romanus">
<emphasis id="B65CF484CEF4220B50A8608211BE80F1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. romanus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
